# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok british professor anthony john allan was on wednesday awarded the #### stockholm water prize handed out each year in the field of water research , the stockholm international water institute said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (r / research-institute
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Stockholm"
                  :op2 "International"
                  :op3 "Water"
                  :op4 "Institute"))
      :ARG1 (a / award-01
            :ARG1 (p / prize
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Stockholm"
                        :op2 "Water"
                        :op3 "Prize")
                  :ARG1-of (h / hand-out-03
                        :frequency (r2 / rate-entity-91
                              :ARG3 (t / temporal-quantity
                                    :quant 1
                                    :unit (y / year)))
                        :topic (f / field
                              :mod (r3 / research-01
                                    :ARG1 (w / water)))))
            :ARG2 (p2 / person
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 " anthony"
                        :op2 "John"
                        :op3 "Allan")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Britain"))
                        :ARG2 (p3 / professor)))
            :time (w2 / wednesday)))

      :time (n3 / now))

                  :ARG2 -)

                                    :op2 "Africa"))

                  :ARG2 (m3 / member)))

            :poss (p4 / port
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Bilbao")

                  :ARG0-of (s2 / specialize-01
                        :ARG1 (d / disaster))
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "U.S.")))
            :ARG2 (p2 / permit-01
                  :ARG1 (e / enter-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (c3 / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Myanmar")
                              :ARG1-of (n4 / neighbor-01))
                        :time (a / after
                              :op1 (s3 / strike-01
                                    :ARG0 (c4 / cyclone
                                          :ARG0-of (d2 / devastate-01)))
                              :quant (m / more-than
                                    :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                                          :quant 1
                                          :unit (m2 / month))))))
            :mod (s4 / still)
            :location c)

            :weekday (t2 / thursday)))

            :ARG0-of (r2 / rebel-01))
      :time d
      :weekday (m4 / monday))

# ::id 1829 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok after opening european championship qualifying with a hard-fought #-# win over estonia , italy is hoping to score more goals against the faeroe islands in florence on tuesday .
# ::alignments
(h / hope-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Italy"))
      :ARG1 (s / score-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (g / goal
                  :quant (m / more))
            :ARG3 (ii / island
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Falkland"
                        :op2 "Islands")
                  :mod (f / faeroe))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / tuesday)))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (q / qualify-02
                  :ARG2 (c2 / championship
                        :mod (c3 / continent
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Europe")))
                  :manner (f2 / fight-01
                        :ARG1-of (h2 / hard-02))))
      :time a
      :op1 (w / win-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG2 ii
            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "Estonia")))

# ::id 1830 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok ethiopian tribesmen invaded a village in northern kenya on monday , killing six people , bringing the total death toll in the retaliatory raids over the last week to ## , police said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / police)
      :ARG1 (ii / invade-01
            :ARG0 (t / tribeman
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Ethiopia")))
            :ARG1 (v / village
                  :location (n2 / north
                        :part-of c
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Kenya"))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday))
      :ARG0-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (b / bring-up-02
                  :ARG1 (t2 / toll
                        :mod (d2 / die-01)
                        :ARG1-of (t3 / total-01)
                        :ARG1-of c2
                        :ARG0 (r / raid-01
                              :ARG2-of (r2 / retaliate-01)
                              :time (w / week
                                    :mod (l / last)))))
            :ARG4 (p2 / person
                  :quant 6)))

# ::id 1831 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok us energy secretary steven chu said thursday he was `` optimistic '' about upcoming climate talks in copenhagen after meeting with chinese officials over the thorny issue of cutting carbon emissions .
# ::alignments

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Steven"
                  :op2 "Chu")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "States"))
                  :ARG2 (s2 / secretary
                        :topic (e / energy))))
      :ARG1 (o / optimistic
            :domain p
            :topic (t / talk-01
                  :topic (c2 / climate)
                  :time (u / upcoming)
                  :location (c3 / city
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Coptenhagen")))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / thursday))
            :time (a / after
                  :op1 (m / meet-03
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (c4 / country
                                          :name (n4 / name
                                                :op1 "China"))
                                    :ARG2 (o2 / official)))
                        :ARG2 (ii / issue-02
                              :ARG0 (c5 / cut-02
                                    :ARG1 (e2 / emit-01
                                          :ARG1 (c6 / carbon)))
                              :mod (t3 / thorny))))))
